sources.title: Sundown (1941) Gene Tierney | Drama, War | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
She was too dangerous to love!
Englishmen fighting Nazis in Africa discover an exotic mystery woman living among the natives and enlist her aid in overcoming the Germans.

Director: Henry Hathaway
Writers: Charles G. Booth, Barré Lyndon
Stars: Gene Tierney, Bruce Cabot, George Sanders & Dorothy Dandridge
Genres: Classics, Drama, War
